WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.260 --> 00:00:02.260
The IOM specifically calls for

00:00:02.260 --> 00:00:05.395
recognizing the home
as a new care setting.

00:00:05.395 --> 00:00:09.930
This aligns with more use of home-based
technologies for monitoring and

00:00:09.930 --> 00:00:11.370
treatment and

00:00:11.370 --> 00:00:15.730
the use of the information technologies
we'll discuss in lesson seven.

00:00:15.730 --> 00:00:19.630
Such as personal health records
to promote patient engagement and

00:00:19.630 --> 00:00:21.600
communication with health professionals.

